## card
### Load remotely
```plantuml

' configures the library
!global $LIB_BASE_LOCATION="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tmorin/plantuml-libs/master/dist"
' loads the library
!include $LIB_BASE_LOCATION/bootstrap.puml
' loads the aws-20200911 bootstrap
include('aws-20200911/bootstrap')
' loads the AmazonQuickSight element
include('aws-20200911/Service/Analytics/AmazonQuickSight')
AmazonQuickSightCard('amazon_quick_sight', 'Amazon Quick Sight', 'Molestiae praesentium aut natus dolorem. Aut consequatur fugiat a consequatur ut.')
@enduml
```
